ed during an exchange of gunfire between armed individuals and police officers, with police claiming Kharroub was part of a group en route to carry out a planned criminal activity. Police announced the deaths of Ghied Kharroub and another individual, the injury of a third, and a police officer sustaining serious injuries.","review_status":"auto","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2025-01-01_2025-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2025-01-01_2025-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":241}